---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Leadership"
  heroTitle="My leadership philosophy"
  heroSubtitle="Empowering teams, driving impact"
>
  <h2>True leadership is servant leadership</h2>
  <p>
    My core belief as a manager is that true leadership is servant leadership. My primary focus is on the success and
    growth of my direct reports. I am committed to creating an environment where each individual feels empowered,
    supported, and challenged to achieve their full potential. This means actively listening, providing constructive
    feedback, advocating for their needs, and removing obstacles so they can do their best work. When my team thrives,
    our research excels.
  </p>

  <h2>Promote a culture of collaboration</h2>
  <p>
    Beyond individual success, I see it as my responsibility to cultivate a culture of collaboration. UX research is
    most impactful when it's integrated seamlessly across the organization. I strive to foster strong partnerships, break
    down silos, and ensure that our research insights are shared effectively and understood broadly.
  </p>
  <p>
    Source:
    <a href={site.links.uxpaArticle} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Aligning UX with business goals</a>
  </p>

  <h2>Align research and business goals</h2>
  <p>
    Ultimately, all our efforts are directed toward a clear purpose: ensuring UX research directly supports and advances
    our business goals. By aligning our research activities with strategic objectives, we not only deliver valuable
    insights but also demonstrate the tangible impact of UX research on the company's success. My role is to bridge the
    gap between user understanding and business outcomes, driving meaningful change through data-informed decisions.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
